title: Jimmy Kimmel joins Facebook, melts hearts with adorable photo...
text:
Awww!
TV host and comedian Jimmy Kimmel joined Facebook on Friday and immediately warmed fans' hearts by posting a sweet photo of himself with his daughter, Jane.
>> Read more trending stories
"Is this where you post photos of babies at the pumpkin patch?" he wrote in the viral post , which has received more than 14,000 likes.
>> Click here to see the post
More than 81,380 users liked Kimmel's page by early Sunday. Check it out here.
Kimmel is the host of "Jimmy Kimmel Live," which airs weeknights on ABC.
